&lt;p&gt;Simplex is looking for analytical and creative individuals to join our trading team.&amp;nbsp; Traders at Simplex work closely with our technology team to design and optimize algorithmic trading strategies based on deep knowledge of market microstructure, trading&amp;nbsp; dynamics, and data-focused understanding of pricing, risk management, and order flow.&amp;nbsp; An ideal candidate is collaborative, strongly self-motivated, and capable of detail-oriented troubleshooting, data analysis, and robust systems design.&lt;/p&gt;
